title: Dave Brubeck - 1994 - Just You, Just Me FLAC
description:
Dave Brubeck - 1994 - Just You, Just Me

It had been nearly 40 years since Dave Brubeck's last solo piano recording when he recorded this relaxed set. Brubeck sounds typically creative yet often wistful on the seven standards, four originals, and a "Tribute to Stephen Foster." This is a fine addition to Brubeck's extensive yet consistently satisfying discography. (AllMusic)
